spark plugs, batteries, shock absorbers, filters, pumps and other spare parts or accessories for personal transport equipment.
Includes: fire extinguishers for transport
equipment; products specifically for the cleaning and maintenance of transport equipment
such as paints, chrome cleaners, sealing compounds and bodywork polishes; covers for
motor cars, motorcycles, etc.
Excludes: crash helmets for motorcycles and
bicycles (03.1.3); non-specific products for
cleaning and maintenance such as distilled
water, household sponges, chamois leathers,
detergents, etc. (05.6.1); charges for the fitting
