07.3.3 Passenger transport by air (S)
– Transport of individuals and groups of persons and luggage by aeroplane and helicopter.
07.3.4 Passenger transport by sea and inland waterway
(S)
– Transport of individuals and groups of persons and luggage by ship, boat, ferry,
